===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|music|lang=en}} An [[electronic]] [[instrument]] that creates its [[sound]]s with electronics and has a [[keyboard]].
# {{context|music|lang=en}} An electronic instrument [[module]] that creates its sounds with electronics and does not have any keyboard.
# {{context|electronics|lang=en}} An electronic [[circuit]] that generates an electronic [[signal]] [[oscillation]] with [[accurate]] [[timing]] from a [[reference]] [[oscillator]].
# {{context|electronics|lang=en}} An electronic [[device]] that generates electronic signal [[pattern]]s to [[test]] an electronic circuit.

